WEBVTT

00:01:00.121 --> 00:01:03.287
Domino bo’lish men uchun, gapirish
va qiyin bo’lgan

00:01:03.329 --> 00:01:05.579
vazifalarnini,
ayniqsa, kerak bo’lgan vaqtda

00:01:05.579 --> 00:01:07.663
boshqa insonlar ergashish umidi bilan

00:01:07.704 --> 00:01:10.079
qilish demakdir.

00:01:11.038 --> 00:01:13.579
Va gap shundaki: men siz o’ylagan

00:01:13.621 --> 00:01:17.079
lekin aytishga jur’at qilolmagan 
fikrni gapiradigan insonman.

00:01:17.121 --> 00:01:19.871
Ko’p bora odamlar bizni qo’rqmas

00:01:19.913 --> 00:01:21.871
deb hisoblaydilar.

00:01:21.913 --> 00:01:23.038
Biz qo’rqmas emasmiz.

00:01:23.079 --> 00:01:25.538
Biz haqiqatni mansabdorlarga
so’ylashimiz

00:01:25.579 --> 00:01:27.788
oqibatlaridan yoki qurbonliklardan

00:01:27.788 --> 00:01:29.788
qo’rqmaymiz emas.
Haqiqat shundaki,

00:01:29.829 --> 00:01:32.038
biz shunday qilishimiz kerakligini 
his qilamiz